OL,3,CJersey police inspector calls for
OL,4,Cammunition at home ban following
OL,5,CBondhi attack
OL,7,FA senior police officer in Jersey is
OL,8,Fcalling for a change in the law to
OL,9,Freduce the risk of extreme gun
OL,10,Fviolence.
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector Chris
OL,13,FBeechey wants to stop recreational
OL,14,Fshooters from storing ammunition at
OL,15,Fhome, but instead at approved clubs.
