OL,3,CJersey police inspector calls for
OL,4,Cammunition at home ban following
OL,5,CBondhi attack
OL,7,FIt follows last month's mass shooting
OL,8,Fon Bondi Beach in Australia, and while
OL,9,Fthe islands have never experienced
OL,10,Fsuch an attack, there are concerns
OL,11,Fover the number of guns registered
OL,12,Fhere.
OL,14,F"There is no need to have any
OL,15,Fammunition in the home environment,"
OL,16,FDCI Beechy told ITV News.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
