OL,3,CJersey police inspector calls for
OL,4,Cammunition at home ban following
OL,5,CBondhi attack
OL,7,F"The reasons why become clear if we
OL,8,Flook at Australia. Weapons are
OL,9,Fdangerous, and they're especially
OL,10,Fdangerous when coupled with
OL,11,Fammunition."
OL,13,FIn Jersey alone, there are more than
OL,14,F8,000 registered firearms, but only
OL,15,F1,100 holders of firearms certificates.
OL,17,FHowever, until the beginning of this
OL,18,Fyear, anyone with a license could ask
OL,19,Fto be allowed 5,000 rounds of
OL,20,Fammunition, which could be stored at
OL,21,Fhome.
