OL,3,CJersey police inspector calls for
OL,4,Cammunition at home ban following
OL,5,CBondhi attack
OL,7,FJersey Police do not know the volume
OL,8,Fof ammunition currently stored in
OL,9,Fislanders' homes.
OL,11,FFrom the beginning of 2026, every
OL,12,Ffirearms certificate that is issued or
OL,13,Frenewed will be given without
OL,14,Fammunition, but the holder can then
OL,15,Fapply to the constable for a "minimal"
OL,16,Famount to hold.
OL,18,FUnder current legislation,
OL,19,Fcertificates can also be issued with
OL,20,Fwritten-in orders not to store
OL,21,Fammunition at home.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
