OL,4,Cammunition at home ban following
OL,5,CBondhi attack
OL,7,FDCI Beechey still believes the law
OL,8,Fcould go further to prevent any risk
OL,9,Fof future harm.
OL,11,F"One of the ways you can significantly
OL,12,Freduce the risk of a tragedy here is
OL,13,Fto remove ammunition from the public
OL,14,Fenvironment," he explained.
OL,16,F"It removes that risk significantly in
OL,17,Fterms of an individual who suffers a
OL,18,Fmental health episode or is
OL,19,Fradicalised in some way.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
