OL,3,CJersey police inspector calls for
OL,4,Cammunition at home ban following
OL,5,CBondhi attack
OL,7,F"If we remove the opportunity for that
OL,8,Ffirearm to actually be used outside of
OL,9,Fa licensed club environment, then that
OL,10,Fhas to be better and more effective
OL,11,Ffor overall island safety."
OL,13,FGuernsey has successfully enforced a
OL,14,Fban on keeping hard cast bullets at
OL,15,Fhome for more than a decade.
