OL,3,CJersey police inspector calls for
OL,4,Cammunition at home ban following
OL,5,CBondhi attack
OL,7,FHowever, some shooting group members
OL,8,Fhave told ITV News of their
OL,9,Ffrustration that when a tragedy such
OL,10,Fas the Bondhi Beach attack occurs, the
OL,11,Fsport they love becomes a target for
OL,12,Fcriticism.
OL,14,FOne member questioned where all of the
OL,15,Fammunition, which would be taken from
OL,16,Fpeople's homes, would be stored.
OL,18,FSome have even compared the proposed
OL,19,Fmove to banning the use of cars on
OL,20,Froads, given the worldwide prevalence
OL,21,Fof terrorism using vehicles as weapons.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
