OL,3,CJersey police inspector calls for
OL,4,Cammunition at home ban following
OL,5,CBondhi attack
OL,7,FIn a statement, Minister for Justice
OL,8,Fand Home Affairs Deputy Mary Le
OL,9,FHegarat said that she has been working
OL,10,Fwith Connetables to develop solutions
OL,11,Fto be implemented by the next
OL,12,Fgovernment.
OL,14,F"I support the proposals concerning
OL,15,Fthe restriction on home storage of
OL,16,Fammunition, and I have discussed this
OL,17,Fwith the Comite previously," the
OL,18,Fminister stated.
