OL,7,F"I understand that the Connetables
OL,8,Fhave agreed to take a much more
OL,9,Frestrictive view on home ammunition
OL,10,Fstorage when granting new licences.
OL,12,F"It is a good step forward in the
OL,13,Fabsence of capacity to make more
OL,14,Ffundamental changes."
